    <h2 class="sect-title">About North Haven</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in the early sixties, the neighborhood is represented by Ward 4 Councilor in the Calgary City Council.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">North Haven lies to the east of Calgaryâ€™s largest municipal reserve, the Nose Hill Park. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in North Haven primarily comprise of single-family detached homes often listed at an average price of $450,000, with a small selection of the more affordable townhomes as well. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Since most of the bungalows were built nearly half a century ago, a majority of the housing units have undergone a series of renovations to match the changing needs of the contemporary homebuyer.</p>
        </div>
